Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.80,0:01:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村 绯村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.97,0:01:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经中午！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.33,0:01:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃饭的时间到！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.24,0:01:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！我在叫你啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.47,0:01:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要不理人啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.38,0:01:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！痛死人了 ！\N头发被你拉掉五根了啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.31,0:02:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你不对\N不好好听别人说话！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.18,0:02:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么\N故意挑林中小径走啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.15,0:02:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定又想把我甩掉 是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.52,0:02:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是\N干嘛赶得那么急！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.29,0:02:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中餐也要吃呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.23,0:02:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是故意挑这种路走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.80,0:02:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是比起折回原路\N直接破林而出会来得比较快罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.87,0:02:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傍晚 就可走出这个森林了 ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.70,0:02:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前\N我可没休息的打算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.97,0:02:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,午饭可以边走边吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.08,0:02:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 那我要吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.68,0:02:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村你呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.82,0:02:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不巧 我没有带任何吃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.52,0:02:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔！但这个是我的\N我可不想与你分享
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.99,0:02:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.12,0:02:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过 要是你告诉我\N苍紫他们的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.86,0:02:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就分一点给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.96,0:02:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.43,0:02:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苍紫他们现在在干嘛呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.97,0:02:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第三十五话\N受控于志志雄魔掌下的村落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.34,0:03:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你说哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.48,0:03:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,般若君总是会照顾\N跟在苍紫身后的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.05,0:03:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有好笑的大福\N胖胖的小太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.29,0:03:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死气沉沉的阿明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.52,0:03:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都闹在一起好不快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.79,0:03:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有蛇啊 危险 小心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.23,0:03:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我受够了\N好心告诉你他们的事你却……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.00,0:03:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你给我好好听着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.63,0:03:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一句话都不说 乱无趣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.30,0:03:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才想缓和这凝重的气氛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.21,0:03:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,旅途上 大家快快乐乐的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.61,0:03:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但就如我之前说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.68,0:03:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有我一人被留在京都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.48,0:03:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和大家共有的回忆\N只有那么一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.82,0:03:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 苍紫君却\N永远活在我的心中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.42,0:03:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家现在都在做什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.22,0:03:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们离开我的时候\N我哭得好伤心……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.40,0:03:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 好好听人家说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.63,0:03:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.70,0:04:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走路都比听我说话来的有趣吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.77,0:04:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你干嘛特别花工夫\N把草丛拨到两边啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.41,0:04:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样才好走啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.52,0:04:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这小子要甩开我的话\N我一定没辄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.72,0:04:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他竟为了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.49,0:04:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,个性虽然完全不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.32,0:04:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但不把内心表露出来的这一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.56,0:04:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒跟苍紫有点像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.96,0:04:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我改变心意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.80,0:04:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肚子很饿吧 绯村？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.13,0:04:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个小圆饼给你吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.34,0:04:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一的一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.27,0:04:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 唯一的一个！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.98,0:04:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？里面会不会放毒药啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.25,0:04:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才没有呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.99,0:04:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村 刚刚好像有什么声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.69,0:04:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保持安静\N离我越远越好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.29,0:05:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说有人要你的命\N莫非是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.80,0:05:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别说了 快走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.86,0:05:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 现在被攻击的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.13,0:05:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定会牵扯到小操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.17,0:05:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没办法\N只好来个先发制人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.54,0:05:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等我啊！我……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.64,0:05:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可也是御庭派的一份子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.44,0:05:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多少可以帮你一点忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.51,0:05:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.59,0:05:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个人死了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.60,0:05:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没 但也快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.03,0:05:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有没有临走前想说的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.57,0:05:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你死前见到你\N也是一种缘份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.44,0:05:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么\N我都会尽力帮你完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.91,0:05:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜…拜托你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.35,0:05:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将我弟弟和村民……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.92,0:05:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从志志雄一帮人手中救出来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.49,0:05:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,志志雄……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.73,0:06:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这儿吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.00,0:06:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 醒了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.64,0:06:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.21,0:06:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我大哥呢 大哥……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.24,0:06:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们看到他时\N他已经…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.52,0:06:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畜牲 畜牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.69,0:06:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可不可以告诉我\N到底是怎么一回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.29,0:06:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉你这个外人\N又有什么用呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.33,0:06:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了会战志志雄\N而朝京都走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.04,0:06:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我住在附近的新月村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.71,0:06:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二年前 \N志志雄的手下突然侵入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.88,0:06:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上就杀了驻扎警官\N占领全村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.98,0:07:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之后又来了一个新警官\N也惨遭毒手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.59,0:07:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从此没有一个警官敢来这
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.35,0:07:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而志志雄的走狗\N一个个进驻村内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.66,0:07:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的新月村…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.17,0:07:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样被政府遗弃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.74,0:07:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被遗弃\N你说得太夸张了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.37,0:07:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们可能正在好好地拟定策略
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.28,0:07:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 这又怎么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.28,0:07:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是大哥从东京带回\N最新的地图
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.31,0:07:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看 已经没有新月村了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.55,0:07:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大哥发现这一点\N觉得整村都怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.29,0:07:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,于是\N决定至少要保住自已的家人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.06,0:07:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到就被杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.03,0:07:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是志志雄直属部下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.43,0:07:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是统治新月村的尖角\N那个王八干的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.84,0:08:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不回村里不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.41,0:08:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,村里还有来不及逃走的爹娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.45,0:08:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大哥已死\N只有我可以救他们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.95,0:08:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大哥 请助我一臂之力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.93,0:08:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我代替你大哥\N助你一臂之力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.00,0:08:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小操\N这小子就拜托你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.80,0:08:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我也要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.77,0:08:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 我一个人去就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.54,0:08:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们在这等着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.98,0:08:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全毫无整顿\N如同废墟一般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.45,0:08:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,志志雄每半年会来这儿一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.06,0:08:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道他是为了什么目的而来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.56,0:08:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了迎接他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.06,0:08:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个村平常才都是由尖角管辖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.97,0:09:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次真巧 志志雄也来到村里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.11,0:09:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尖角要款待志志雄 \N现在应该在行馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.88,0:09:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要救出我爹娘的话\N只有趁现在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.92,0:09:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.35,0:09:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不靠近一点 会跟丢喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.19,0:09:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白痴 绯村可不是一般人唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.79,0:09:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再走近一点就会被他发现的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.13,0:09:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村这家伙\N什么事都一个人扛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.43,0:09:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是御庭派的出身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.63,0:09:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要帮你也是绰绰有余的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.45,0:09:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和那小孩的哥哥一样\N全身被砍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.42,0:09:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这也是尖角搞的鬼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.46,0:10:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爹！娘！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.12,0:10:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些外人\N不可让外人活着回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.75,0:10:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么把他们杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.99,0:10:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那小鬼一家人想从村里逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.03,0:10:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了追究责任\N尖角大人才将他们处死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.47,0:10:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是把他们吊上去的是我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.04,0:10:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是…杀鸡儆猴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.24,0:10:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这儿是伟大的志志雄陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.31,0:10:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从那些猪脑政府官手中夺来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.54,0:10:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这儿的生杀大权\N都操于志志雄陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.15,0:10:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和管理这儿的尖角大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.82,0:10:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尖角大人下令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.49,0:10:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外人只有死路一条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.85,0:11:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觉悟吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.82,0:11:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该觉悟的是你们这些人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.23,0:11:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平常我可不喜欢看人流血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.54,0:11:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是今天这个样子\N我只得…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.94,0:11:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀得你们一个不留
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.69,0:11:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 振作一点嘛 喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.89,0:11:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你很难过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.50,0:11:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在可不是\N躲在一旁畏缩的时候啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.47,0:11:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么哭\N死人也不会活过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.80,0:11:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在赶紧振奋起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.34,0:11:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听我的话嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.14,0:11:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外人只有死路一条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.58,0:11:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.51,0:12:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外人只有……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.18,0:12:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死路一条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.03,0:12:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.40,0:12:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为那家伙去京都了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.83,0:12:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到还在这儿混
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.87,0:12:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这名警官…是绯村的朋友吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.54,0:12:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斋藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.58,0:12:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.55,0:12:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.35,0:12:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工作呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.25,0:12:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在这儿的眼线告诉我\N志志雄现在人在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.09,0:12:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要等到讨伐军来到\N可能还要花些时日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.96,0:12:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才来附近晃一晃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.96,0:12:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我那名眼线现在下落不明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.43,0:12:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道会是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.87,0:12:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那名少年的哥哥\N难道是警局的密探吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.37,0:12:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少年… 原来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.97,0:13:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三岛荣一郎是新月村的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.51,0:13:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难怪毫不被怀疑的\N就能潜入村内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.98,0:13:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是身份曝光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.32,0:13:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才死命地要守住家人性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.95,0:13:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是笨蛋一个\N为什么不等到我来……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.59,0:13:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  自已的部下死了 \N还说那种话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.93,0:13:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你懂什么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.78,0:13:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小臭鼬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.48,0:13:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去死啦\N杀死你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.45,0:13:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看我贯杀招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.85,0:13:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦\N他就是那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.42,0:13:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟他计较那么多\N可是没完没了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.69,0:13:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.87,0:14:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赶快把尸体卸下来\N好好忌吊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.17,0:14:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.24,0:14:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.91,0:14:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可把尸体拿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.04,0:14:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.55,0:14:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说拿就拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.75,0:14:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,万一冒犯了尖角大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.28,0:14:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们全村都不得好死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.92,0:14:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尖角大人没有批准的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.92,0:14:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就维持原样吊着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.16,0:14:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡说些什么呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.82,0:14:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们不是同乡吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.86,0:14:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们下场如此悲惨\N你们还对尖角千依百顺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.30,0:14:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反抗尖角只有死路一条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.43,0:14:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不反抗他 尚可苟且偷生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.87,0:14:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再把事情闹大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.57,0:14:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了全村着想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.01,0:14:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些外人和三岛家的人\N现在就滚出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.01,0:14:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听到了吗 荣次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.22,0:14:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王八
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.72,0:14:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别动怒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.06,0:14:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会赔上性命\N维护人的骄傲与尊严的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.13,0:15:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本来就很少有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.90,0:15:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要苟延残喘过一生的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.86,0:15:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪需要什么骄傲、尊严
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.50,0:15:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随你怎么说\N你们外人是不会了解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.67,0:15:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不是因为你们这些警察没用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.54,0:15:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.41,0:15:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正\N我不准任何人卸下尸体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.14,0:15:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们快给我滚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.28,0:15:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.17,0:15:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.17,0:15:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.50,0:15:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在干吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.68,0:15:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个村庄若是灭亡的话\N都是你们害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.15,0:15:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外人还敢说呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.39,0:15:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀人魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.22,0:16:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个村子已经变成这样啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.26,0:16:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是志志雄理想中\N新时代的…日本吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.73,0:16:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人类都害怕暴力\N在其统治之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.04,0:16:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有求生是唯一重要的事\N没有骄傲、尊严
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.57,0:16:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斋藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.84,0:16:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,政府当局真的放弃\N这个村落了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.35,0:16:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只这个村落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.31,0:16:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经有十个村落被遗弃\N而成了志志雄的领土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.32,0:16:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警局也不想再插手管事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.22,0:16:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是不太懂啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.19,0:16:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 警察不行的话\N不是还有军队吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.23,0:16:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨瓜 西南战争才开打半年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.06,0:16:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若出动军队镇压内乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.63,0:16:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我国内政之混乱\N会被各国摸得一清二楚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.37,0:16:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在可不是说那种话的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.04,0:16:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算想出兵\N也得不到官僚的首肯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.81,0:17:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.18,0:17:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都害怕\N大久保公卿的事件再度上演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.49,0:17:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,政府官僚也是人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.25,0:17:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁不怜惜自己的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.66,0:17:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底有谁\N真能为我们做点事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.46,0:17:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁啊 谁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.50,0:17:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道没人真正关心这个村子吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.06,0:17:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底有谁能让这孩子一扫阴霾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.97,0:17:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的…我一个人来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.48,0:17:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.28,0:17:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是村子 \N警方 军队 政府
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.85,0:17:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都会受控于志志雄的手下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.52,0:17:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以此刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.16,0:17:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该是我和你这种人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.73,0:17:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起替天行道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.93,0:17:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道志志雄的行馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.57,0:17:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没到京都那么远\N现在去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.54,0:17:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.24,0:18:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我也要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.61,0:18:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能去 给我待在这
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.58,0:18:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.71,0:18:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也无法容忍\N干出那种事的坏蛋呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.42,0:18:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小操小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.42,0:18:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.45,0:18:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管谁说什么 我都要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.02,0:18:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你给我待在荣次的身旁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.24,0:18:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.17,0:18:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村拔刀斋那个家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.78,0:18:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在箱根山顶时\N突然潜进森林中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.58,0:18:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才不小心跟丢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.15,0:18:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会再派人全力搜索的\N所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.05,0:18:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么处置呢\N志志雄陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.22,0:18:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了 放过他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.82,0:18:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,半年没泡温泉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.89,0:18:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉真舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.89,0:18:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我还没改变主意以前\N快把拔刀斋给我找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.00,0:19:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢主隆恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.77,0:19:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.87,0:19:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是下次再犯的话\N我可饶不了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.21,0:19:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.68,0:19:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,濑田大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.75,0:19:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 什么事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.02,0:19:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.55,0:19:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.06,0:19:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,志志雄陛下 志志雄陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.62,0:19:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了 又怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.36,0:19:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脖子左边带有十字伤痕的男子\N和配带日本刀的警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.40,0:19:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像正朝着我们的行馆而来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.24,0:19:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.77,0:19:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还没去登堂拜礼\N他们就先来了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.27,0:19:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是道上前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.58,0:19:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宗次郎 你出去迎接
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.21,0:19:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.31,0:19:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顺便叫尖角随时备战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.65,0:19:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尖角不管何时\N都处于备战状态呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.70,0:20:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.87,0:20:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你拿那个 要去哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.21,0:20:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去志志雄的行馆\N我要报仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.68,0:20:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么鬼话啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.94,0:20:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不行的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.05,0:20:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是行不行的问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.45,0:20:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是看你做不做而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.88,0:20:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我只有一个人\N才不会怕死呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.19,0:20:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.32,0:20:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又怎么了\N你要阻止我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.09,0:20:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌\N笨瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.99,0:20:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,志志雄的行馆里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.33,0:20:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可不是只有尖角一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.46,0:20:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有志志雄的亲信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.60,0:20:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然\N刚刚的蒙面部队也会在那
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.20,0:20:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 还没进去\N就给人家踢出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.64,0:20:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.07,0:20:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我决定要帮你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.61,0:20:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能感受你的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.38,0:20:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天若换成是御庭派的人被杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.42,0:20:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也会不顾性命去讨血债的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.02,0:21:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了 绯村\N我决定要帮这孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.06,0:21:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以跟着我\N但可别碍手碍脚的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.14,0:21:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们就是\N绯村拔刀斋和斋藤一吧
